				<div class="hvres-meaning small">• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/%E1%BA%A4t-H%E1%BB%A3i-ni%C3%AAn-ng%C5%A9-nguy%E1%BB%87t-k%C3%ADnh-%C4%91%E1%BB%99c-%C4%91%E1%BB%93ng-t%C3%B4n-t%C6%B0%C6%A1ng-t%E1%BA%BF-ph%E1%BA%A3-ph%E1%BA%A3-tr%C6%B0%E1%BB%9Fng-L%E1%BA%A1c-Vi%C3%AAn-T%C3%B4n-Th%E1%BA%A5t-%C4%90%C3%A0n-ti%C3%AAn-sinh/poem-KtNHYtao7xkVxtfQeKzt4Q">Ất Hợi niên ngũ nguyệt kính độc đồng tôn tương tế phả phả trưởng Lạc Viên Tôn Thất Đàn tiên sinh “Thận độc ngôn chí” thi hoạ vận dĩ đáp - 乙亥年五月敬讀同尊相濟譜譜長樂園尊室檀先生慎獨言志詩和韻以答</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Nguy%E1%BB%85n-Ph%C3%BAc-%C6%AFng-B%C3%ACnh/author-eQ6wft6d1E9_uEITUaRRlg">Nguyễn Phúc Ưng Bình</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/B%E1%BA%AFc-m%C3%B4n-3/poem-bWu-F5mgUfzC84dUKldNdA">Bắc môn 3 - 北門 3</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/Canh-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-ni%C3%AAn-ch%E1%BA%BF/poem-x1HY9Hmqz-E6-xMz9JnWwA">Canh Tuất niên chế - 庚戌年製</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Do%C3%A3n-Khu%C3%AA/author-ueZqmqDIif0v3prANC9aXg">Doãn Khuê</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/%C4%90%E1%BA%A1i-B%E1%BA%A3o-tam-ni%C3%AAn-Nh%C3%A2m-Tu%E1%BA%A5t-khoa-ti%E1%BA%BFn-s%C4%A9-%C4%91%E1%BB%81-danh-k%C3%BD/poem-lmPI_Y7GazogxyWzI82qMg">Đại Bảo tam niên Nhâm Tuất khoa tiến sĩ đề danh ký - 大寶弎年壬戌科進士題名記</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/%C4%90%C3%B4ng-S%C6%A1n-1/poem-uBPU4KiEiLcvafcVu9ItPg">Đông Sơn 1 - 東山1</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Kh%E1%BB%95ng-T%E1%BB%AD/author-Ghtg3UHpaIYXCkHiqunT7w">Khổng Tử</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Ki%E1%BB%81u-L%C4%83ng-thi-tam-th%E1%BA%ADp-v%E1%BA%ADn-nh%C3%A2n-tr%C3%ACnh-huy%E1%BB%87n-n%E1%BB%99i-ch%C6%B0-quan/poem-iMd00tDBdT14eExlDSnUyw">Kiều Lăng thi tam thập vận, nhân trình huyện nội chư quan - 橋陵詩三十韻，因呈縣內諸官</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/Ph%E1%BB%A5ng-ho%E1%BA%A1-ng%E1%BB%B1-ch%E1%BA%BF-Qu%C3%A2n-minh-th%E1%BA%A7n-l%C6%B0%C6%A1ng/poem-97NXg2ioTsrdqyKRAOQPEg">Phụng hoạ ngự chế “Quân minh thần lương” - 奉和御製君明臣良</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/Th%C3%A2n-Nh%C3%A2n-Trung/author-eOFIe3QgfrDzlduYauxtuQ">Thân Nhân Trung</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/T%E1%BA%B7ng-T%E1%BB%AB-C%C3%A1n/poem-TMDCykIDLkn2ovF5EJROGQ">Tặng Từ Cán - 贈徐幹</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/T%C3%A0o-Th%E1%BB%B1c/author-3mdeOfneLQCMOxlLrV12_w">Tào Thực</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/Th%E1%BB%8B-t%C3%B2ng-t%C3%B4n-T%E1%BA%BF/poem-IT-lvhqSGw2uNWQEoMNJqQ">Thị tòng tôn Tế - 示從孫濟</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/%C4%90%E1%BB%97-Ph%E1%BB%A7/author-Se3x2jWTezvoDpkpSU9qjg">Đỗ Phủ</a>)<br/>• <a target="_blank" href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/V%C4%83n-t%E1%BA%BF-th%E1%BA%A7n-s%C3%A1ch/poem-jodinZfi6gur7Teb7mLN4w">Văn tế thần sách - 祭書神文</a> (<a href="https://www.thivien.net/L%E1%BB%97-T%E1%BA%A5n/author-TXAaCmjdRWIV6MkCYE1psQ">Lỗ Tấn</a>)<br/></div>	</div>
